seo: Apache HTTPD,mod_jk,敏感信息泄漏漏洞
summary: 检测Apache HTTPD mod_jk是否存在敏感信息泄漏漏洞，通过构造特定请求检查是否能绕过访问控制并获取JK状态管理信息。
summary_en: Detect whether there is a sensitive information leakage vulnerability in Apache HTTPD mod_jk, and check if constructed requests can bypass access control and obtain JK status management information.
